title: Bienvenido al Paraíso - Uvita y Ojochal, Costa Rica
description: Descubre la belleza natural y el estilo de vida vibrante de Uvita y Ojochal, Costa Rica. Tu guía para playas, vida silvestre y vida sostenible en la costa pacífica sur de Costa Rica.
locale: es
permalink: /es/
---

<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>{{ translations.es.home.hero.title }}</h1>
        <p>{{ translations.es.home.hero.subtitle }}</p>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>{{ translations.es.home.welcome }}</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            {% for card in featuredCards_es.cards %}
                <div class="card hover-lift">
                    {% if card.image %}
                        <img src="{{ card.image }}" alt="{{ card.title }}" loading="lazy">
                        {% endif %}
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <h3>{{ card.title }}</h3>
                            <p>{{ card.description }}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    {# Latest stories section - currently disabled
      {% if collections.posts_es %}
        <section class="section alternate">
          <div class="container">
            <h2>{{ translations.es.home.latestStories }}</h2>
            <div class="grid">
              {% for post in collections.posts_es | reverse | limit(3) %}
                <div class="card">
                  {% if post.data.image %}
                    <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
                  {% endif %}
                  <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
                    <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="button">{{ translations.es.home.readMore }}</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      {% endif %}
    #}
